"{\"uid\": \"fansided.com-posts-best-getty-images-2024-paris-olympics-week-1\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Between the Opening and Closing Ceremonies of the2024 Paris Olympics,Getty Imageswill have a team of more than 80 photographers shootingas many as 5 million images.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 54, \"end\": 68, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 69, \"end\": 74, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.999999996862698, \"rank\": 3.135840117645117e-09, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Opening and Closing Ceremonies\", \"from\": 8, \"to\": 42}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 91, \"to\": 97}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 80 photographers\", \"from\": 101, \"to\": 127}, {\"ngram\": \"many as 5 million images\", \"from\": 139, \"to\": 163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those breathtaking photos are then run through a team of more than 40 editors, live-editing remotely from offices in London.\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 282, \"end\": 288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999999745341, \"rank\": 2.5226996463607127e-11, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those breathtaking photos\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 190}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 218}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 40 editors\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 242}, {\"ngram\": \"offices\", \"from\": 271, \"to\": 278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a massive undertaking, a complex amalgamation of human ingenuity and artistic vision with radical technology \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 top-of-the-line lenses, remote cameras, robotic and underwater cameras and more.\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a massive undertaking\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 317}, {\"ngram\": \"a complex amalgamation\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 341}, {\"ngram\": \"human ingenuity\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 360}, {\"ngram\": \"artistic vision\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"the-line\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"remote cameras\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 447}, {\"ngram\": \"robotic and underwater cameras\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The results are breathtaking and help bring all the emotion of excitement of the games to people around around the world.\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 612, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The results\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"all the emotion\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 564}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 577}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 587}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"FanSided is lucky enough to be partnering with Getty throughout these games and each week several photographers will be sharing some of their favorite photos with us and explaining the stories behind them.\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 613, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FanSided\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"FanSided\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FanSided\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FanSided\"}, {\"begin\": 660, \"end\": 665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.999999996862698, \"rank\": 3.135840117645117e-09, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these games\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"several photographers\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 724}, {\"ngram\": \"their favorite photos\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"the stories\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are Steph Chambers, Sarah Stier and Patrick Smith sharing what they captured in the first week.\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 829, \"end\": 834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\", \"score\": 0.9999998189423587, \"rank\": 1.8096332273536294e-07, \"text\": \"Steph\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Scully\"}, {\"begin\": 845, \"end\": 850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\", \"score\": 0.9997271118023927, \"rank\": 0.0002562277186369363, \"text\": \"Sarah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 861, \"end\": 868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\", \"score\": 0.999999987406227, \"rank\": 1.2593736793807875e-08, \"text\": \"Patrick\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patrick_Star\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first week\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay tuned for a full round up of all the best images from the games after the closing ceremonies.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a full round\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"all the best images\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 989}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremonies\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 Olympics is my second time photographing table tennis.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1031, \"end\": 1044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my second time\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"table tennis\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the Tokyo 2020 Games, I covered all 14 days of competition so I am now quite familiar with the sport and some of the athlete's tendencies, which can come as an advantage when anticipating action.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1293, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo 2020 Games\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1118}, {\"ngram\": \"all 14 days\", \"from\": 1130, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete's tendencies\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"an advantage\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, a major component I challenge myself with is patiently waiting for the ball with the Olympics logo to be upright and visible.This can be very tedious!\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a major component\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1322}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1380}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics logo\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Oftentimes, I do not get lucky, but when I do it's quite rewarding.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another challenging part is the backgrounds aren\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t always the cleanest.\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another challenging part\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1549}, {\"ngram\": \"the backgrounds\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The key is to find a spot where the light falls off enough to create a dark background away from referees, LED boards, and other distracting components.\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The key\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"the light\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"a dark background\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"referees\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1704}, {\"ngram\": \"LED boards\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"other distracting components\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The venue has field of play positions so you can get fairly close to the athletes along the sides of the table.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1863, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The venue\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1761}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1771}, {\"ngram\": \"play positions\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1833}, {\"ngram\": \"the sides\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1849}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I prefer to sit on the ground instead of designated photo benches because the lower my line of sight is, the cleaner my backgrounds become.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 2003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"designated photo benches\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"the lower my line\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"sight\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1964}, {\"ngram\": \"my backgrounds\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 1995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, crouching all day for four sessions of table tennis is quite painful.\\u00c2 The sport can be quite repetitive, which can be a disadvantage and advantage depending on how you see it.\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2190, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four sessions\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2048}, {\"ngram\": \"table tennis\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2083}, {\"ngram\": \"The sport\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2093}, {\"ngram\": \"a disadvantage\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"advantage\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The disadvantage is that the photos can look the same if you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re not pushing yourself by finding new ideas.\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2299, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The disadvantage\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"the photos\", \"from\": 2216, \"to\": 2226}, {\"ngram\": \"you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2256}, {\"ngram\": \"new ideas\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the advantage is that you see an interesting serve or reaction many times over.\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the advantage\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"an interesting serve\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2354}, {\"ngram\": \"reaction\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This allows for multiple tries to nail your idea.\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2433, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"multiple tries\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2414}, {\"ngram\": \"your idea\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have primarily been shooting aquatics at the Paris La Defense Arena and Aquatics Centre covering swimming and diving events and medal ceremonies.\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"aquatics\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris La Defense Arena and Aquatics Centre\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2524}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming and diving events\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2560}, {\"ngram\": \"medal ceremonies\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Games brings together these incredible athletes to compete on the world\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s biggest stage\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093providing all the action, but also pure emotion.\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2600}, {\"ngram\": \"these incredible athletes\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2642}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2670}, {\"ngram\": \"all the action\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's unique to get to witness and capture such great emotions in one place, seeing the determination, joy, pride, resilience, exhaustion, agony, heartbreak, among others, of teams and athletes competing for their countries at such a high level.\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2980, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such great emotions\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2797}, {\"ngram\": \"one place\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2810}, {\"ngram\": \"the determination\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2836}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 2838, \"to\": 2841}, {\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2848}, {\"ngram\": \"resilience\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"exhaustion\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2872}, {\"ngram\": \"agony\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2879}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2905}, {\"ngram\": \"teams\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2915}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2928}, {\"ngram\": \"their countries\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 2958}, {\"ngram\": \"such a high level\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 2979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Working on a team of photographers for aquatic events, especially swimming, allows for us to capture so many different angles and perspectives of the competition from above and under the surface.\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 3177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 2999}, {\"ngram\": \"photographers\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3016}, {\"ngram\": \"aquatic events\", \"from\": 3021, \"to\": 3035}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3069, \"to\": 3071}, {\"ngram\": \"so many different angles\", \"from\": 3083, \"to\": 3107}, {\"ngram\": \"perspectives\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3124}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 3128, \"to\": 3143}, {\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am always confident if I don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t think of something or am not in the best position for a moment, someone else on the the team will have it covered.\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3231}, {\"ngram\": \"the best position\", \"from\": 3245, \"to\": 3262}, {\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3275}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3284}, {\"ngram\": \"the the team\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This allows us to really get creative and use the water, action and emotion to create compelling imagery.\", \"from\": 3328, \"to\": 3433, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3340, \"to\": 3342}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 3374, \"to\": 3383}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3391}, {\"ngram\": \"emotion\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3403}, {\"ngram\": \"compelling imagery\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are two of my favorite photos and moments so far.\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my favorite photos\", \"from\": 3451, \"to\": 3469}, {\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In this photo, Gretchen Walsh is just popping out of the water on the second length of the 100m Butterfly Final.\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3506, \"end\": 3520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gretchen Walsh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this photo\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3504}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 3544, \"to\": 3553}, {\"ngram\": \"the second length\", \"from\": 3557, \"to\": 3574}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m Butterfly Final\", \"from\": 3578, \"to\": 3602}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a sprint event, and I feel that this photo freezes her face in such a way that you can almost feel the power that she is bringing to the surface as she breaks out of the surface.\", \"from\": 3604, \"to\": 3790, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sprint event\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3626}, {\"ngram\": \"this photo\", \"from\": 3644, \"to\": 3654}, {\"ngram\": \"her face\", \"from\": 3663, \"to\": 3671}, {\"ngram\": \"such a way\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3685}, {\"ngram\": \"the power\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3720}, {\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 3745, \"to\": 3756}, {\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 3789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Originally I was hoping to get a photo that captured a \\\"bubble\\\" of water over her head just before the breakout, but in this moment, which is just slightly later, I like the way the water just wraps around her face and back.\", \"from\": 3792, \"to\": 4016, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a photo\", \"from\": 3823, \"to\": 3830}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"bubble\", \"from\": 3845, \"to\": 3854}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 3859, \"to\": 3864}, {\"ngram\": \"her head\", \"from\": 3870, \"to\": 3878}, {\"ngram\": \"the breakout\", \"from\": 3891, \"to\": 3903}, {\"ngram\": \"this moment\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 3923}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 3962, \"to\": 3969}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 3970, \"to\": 3979}, {\"ngram\": \"her face\", \"from\": 3998, \"to\": 4006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite being a moment of peak action, I love the delicacy that the water draping over her adds to the image.\", \"from\": 4017, \"to\": 4126, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 4031, \"to\": 4039}, {\"ngram\": \"peak action\", \"from\": 4043, \"to\": 4054}, {\"ngram\": \"the delicacy\", \"from\": 4063, \"to\": 4075}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 4081, \"to\": 4090}, {\"ngram\": \"the image\", \"from\": 4116, \"to\": 4125}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew Gretchen would be a great opportunity to make a photograph like this as she has a really unique stroke and incredible power \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 she is the world record holder in this event.\", \"from\": 4127, \"to\": 4307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4134, \"end\": 4142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"score\": 0.9999999995407052, \"rank\": 4.5914848063420053e-10, \"text\": \"Gretchen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gretchen_Walsh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great opportunity\", \"from\": 4152, \"to\": 4171}, {\"ngram\": \"a photograph\", \"from\": 4180, \"to\": 4192}, {\"ngram\": \"a really unique stroke\", \"from\": 4214, \"to\": 4236}, {\"ngram\": \"incredible power\", \"from\": 4241, \"to\": 4257}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\", \"from\": 4258, \"to\": 4261}, {\"ngram\": \"the world record holder\", \"from\": 4269, \"to\": 4292}, {\"ngram\": \"this event\", \"from\": 4296, \"to\": 4306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We knew going in that Leon would be a big story of the Olympics \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 he is quickly becoming one of the best swimmers we have seen in a while, and being French himself, he has the whole crowd behind him.\", \"from\": 4309, \"to\": 4510, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Leon\", \"from\": 4331, \"to\": 4335}, {\"ngram\": \"a big story\", \"from\": 4345, \"to\": 4356}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\", \"from\": 4360, \"to\": 4376}, {\"ngram\": \"the best swimmers\", \"from\": 4407, \"to\": 4424}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole crowd\", \"from\": 4483, \"to\": 4498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During his race in the Men's 400m Individual Medley final, I wanted to try to make photos that were more creative rather than more traditional, stock swimming photos.\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4677, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his race\", \"from\": 4518, \"to\": 4526}, {\"ngram\": \"photos\", \"from\": 4594, \"to\": 4600}, {\"ngram\": \"more traditional, stock swimming photos\", \"from\": 4637, \"to\": 4676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When he began the second length of breaststroke, I saw that he and the competitors behind him were forming a nice pattern each time they came up to breathe.\", \"from\": 4679, \"to\": 4835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the second length\", \"from\": 4693, \"to\": 4710}, {\"ngram\": \"breaststroke\", \"from\": 4714, \"to\": 4726}, {\"ngram\": \"the competitors\", \"from\": 4746, \"to\": 4761}, {\"ngram\": \"a nice pattern\", \"from\": 4786, \"to\": 4800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not have a lot of time to make this picture because each athlete has their own pace, and so while they may look like they are in sync one moment, they will quickly fall out of sync again.\", \"from\": 4836, \"to\": 5030, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 4852, \"to\": 4857}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 4861, \"to\": 4865}, {\"ngram\": \"this picture\", \"from\": 4874, \"to\": 4886}, {\"ngram\": \"each athlete\", \"from\": 4895, \"to\": 4907}, {\"ngram\": \"their own pace\", \"from\": 4912, \"to\": 4926}, {\"ngram\": \"sync\", \"from\": 4972, \"to\": 4976}, {\"ngram\": \"sync\", \"from\": 5019, \"to\": 5023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I saw the pattern forming, tried to get it, but missed.\", \"from\": 5031, \"to\": 5086, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pattern\", \"from\": 5037, \"to\": 5048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I kept watching and eventually, they came back in sync one more time which made for a nice image that showed Leon in the lead, with a formation of swimmers behind him, all within the rule of thirds.\\u00c2 During the Paris Olympics, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll primarily be covering athletics, otherwise known as track and field.\", \"from\": 5087, \"to\": 5390, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sync\", \"from\": 5137, \"to\": 5141}, {\"ngram\": \"a nice image\", \"from\": 5171, \"to\": 5183}, {\"ngram\": \"Leon\", \"from\": 5196, \"to\": 5200}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead\", \"from\": 5204, \"to\": 5212}, {\"ngram\": \"a formation\", \"from\": 5219, \"to\": 5230}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 5234, \"to\": 5242}, {\"ngram\": \"the rule\", \"from\": 5266, \"to\": 5274}, {\"ngram\": \"thirds\", \"from\": 5278, \"to\": 5284}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 5285, \"to\": 5286}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 5294, \"to\": 5312}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ll\", \"from\": 5314, \"to\": 5320}, {\"ngram\": \"athletics\", \"from\": 5343, \"to\": 5352}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 5373, \"to\": 5378}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 5383, \"to\": 5388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But before that starts, I was assigned to cover a few days of fencing which I was excited about!\", \"from\": 5391, \"to\": 5487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few days\", \"from\": 5439, \"to\": 5449}, {\"ngram\": \"fencing\", \"from\": 5453, \"to\": 5460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As an American, we don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t photograph fencing on a regular basis, so going into a global, major event like the Olympics, I had to quickly relearn the athletes and rules of the sport to ensure I was capturing the action, emotion and peak moments happening throughout the competition.\", \"from\": 5488, \"to\": 5770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5494, \"end\": 5502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999999958779882, \"rank\": 2.9984661119707674e-08, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fencing\", \"from\": 5526, \"to\": 5533}, {\"ngram\": \"a regular basis\", \"from\": 5537, \"to\": 5552}, {\"ngram\": \"a global, major event\", \"from\": 5568, \"to\": 5589}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5595, \"to\": 5607}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 5634, \"to\": 5646}, {\"ngram\": \"rules\", \"from\": 5651, \"to\": 5656}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 5660, \"to\": 5669}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 5696, \"to\": 5706}, {\"ngram\": \"emotion\", \"from\": 5708, \"to\": 5715}, {\"ngram\": \"peak moments\", \"from\": 5720, \"to\": 5732}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 5754, \"to\": 5769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a photographer, the internal memory is always sparked with joy when we realize how amazing this sport is to photograph.\", \"from\": 5771, \"to\": 5893, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a photographer\", \"from\": 5774, \"to\": 5788}, {\"ngram\": \"the internal memory\", \"from\": 5790, \"to\": 5809}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 5833, \"to\": 5836}, {\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 5865, \"to\": 5875}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s unique about photographing fencing is the precision of it.\", \"from\": 5895, \"to\": 5962, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 5895, \"to\": 5903}, {\"ngram\": \"photographing fencing\", \"from\": 5917, \"to\": 5938}, {\"ngram\": \"the precision\", \"from\": 5942, \"to\": 5955}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Much like photography, the sport is about the decisive moment.\", \"from\": 5963, \"to\": 6025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"photography\", \"from\": 5973, \"to\": 5984}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 5986, \"to\": 5995}, {\"ngram\": \"the decisive moment\", \"from\": 6005, \"to\": 6024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's when to attack or when to push the shutter button.\", \"from\": 6026, \"to\": 6081, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shutter button\", \"from\": 6062, \"to\": 6080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because of this, it makes the sport interesting to shoot.\", \"from\": 6082, \"to\": 6139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 6108, \"to\": 6117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because of this, the approach is much different from the typical sports I cover.\", \"from\": 6140, \"to\": 6220, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the approach\", \"from\": 6157, \"to\": 6169}, {\"ngram\": \"the typical sports\", \"from\": 6193, \"to\": 6211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While in many ways like an indoor sport, say basketball, where you are confined to a spot, fencing allows for more freedom in creativity.\", \"from\": 6222, \"to\": 6359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many ways\", \"from\": 6231, \"to\": 6240}, {\"ngram\": \"an indoor sport\", \"from\": 6246, \"to\": 6261}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 6267, \"to\": 6277}, {\"ngram\": \"a spot\", \"from\": 6305, \"to\": 6311}, {\"ngram\": \"more freedom\", \"from\": 6332, \"to\": 6344}, {\"ngram\": \"creativity\", \"from\": 6348, \"to\": 6358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are looking for the exact moment a point is scored.\", \"from\": 6360, \"to\": 6414, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the exact moment\", \"from\": 6379, \"to\": 6395}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 6396, \"to\": 6403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are looking for a big picture to help tell the story of the environment.\", \"from\": 6415, \"to\": 6490, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big picture\", \"from\": 6434, \"to\": 6447}, {\"ngram\": \"the story\", \"from\": 6461, \"to\": 6470}, {\"ngram\": \"the environment\", \"from\": 6474, \"to\": 6489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And what is most unique, is that every point draws a lot of emotions which always translates into compelling imagery.\", \"from\": 6491, \"to\": 6608, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every point\", \"from\": 6524, \"to\": 6535}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 6542, \"to\": 6547}, {\"ngram\": \"emotions\", \"from\": 6551, \"to\": 6559}, {\"ngram\": \"compelling imagery\", \"from\": 6589, \"to\": 6607}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The atmosphere of fans, especially for the French at this year\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Games, also builds the energy in that when a final comes, everyone can feel the tension.\\u00c2 A challenge more generally with sport can be learning a venue.\", \"from\": 6609, \"to\": 6829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6652, \"end\": 6658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9088590801552479, \"rank\": 0.08976664771078914, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The atmosphere\", \"from\": 6609, \"to\": 6623}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 6627, \"to\": 6631}, {\"ngram\": \"this year\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Games\", \"from\": 6662, \"to\": 6681}, {\"ngr