ue is an absolute gem of a venue.\", \"from\": 7094, \"to\": 7135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This venue\", \"from\": 7094, \"to\": 7104}, {\"ngram\": \"an absolute gem\", \"from\": 7108, \"to\": 7123}, {\"ngram\": \"a venue\", \"from\": 7127, \"to\": 7134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boasting beautiful, high ceilings it certainly gives off a grand view.\", \"from\": 7136, \"to\": 7206, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"beautiful, high ceilings\", \"from\": 7145, \"to\": 7169}, {\"ngram\": \"a grand view\", \"from\": 7193, \"to\": 7205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Deciding to a risk, I used a super wide fish shy that creates a circular-like image to really showcase the size and majestic view, with the athletes in mid-competition.\", \"from\": 7207, \"to\": 7375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a risk\", \"from\": 7219, \"to\": 7225}, {\"ngram\": \"a super wide fish\", \"from\": 7234, \"to\": 7251}, {\"ngram\": \"a circular-like image\", \"from\": 7269, \"to\": 7290}, {\"ngram\": \"the size\", \"from\": 7310, \"to\": 7318}, {\"ngram\": \"majestic view\", \"from\": 7323, \"to\": 7336}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 7343, \"to\": 7355}, {\"ngram\": \"mid\", \"from\": 7359, \"to\": 7362}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 7363, \"to\": 7374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This second image is all about Mohamed Elsayed of Team Egypt.\", \"from\": 7377, \"to\": 7438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7408, \"end\": 7423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Elsayed\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mohamed Elsayed\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Elsayed\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mohamed_Elsayed\"}, {\"begin\": 7432, \"end\": 7437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"score\": 0.6670368645538884, \"rank\": 0.4869510005779225, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http:/